posting_body: ["Welcome to San Anselmo's finest apartment community", 'Peaceful, private, perfect!', 'Situated on lushly landscaped grounds, our beautifully maintained property is within easy walking distance of shopping, schools, parks, restaurants, hiking trails and transportation.', 'Spacious one and two bedroom apartments feature large redwood decks, plentiful closet/ storage space, and newly remodeled granite/stainless steel equipped kitchens.', 'All two bedrooms feature wood burning fireplaces.', 'Many units boast majestic views.', 'Come by today to see why our residents love coming home to Parkside!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 12', 'OR Text', '12', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 1060 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Majestic views*', '- Peaceful, private, perfect!', '- Amazing School Districts', '- Pet Friendly', '- Wood burning fireplaces*', '- Large redwood decks', '- Parking Included', '- Newly remolded granite/stainless steel equipped kitchens', '- Plentiful closet/ storage space', 'Community Amenities', '- Corn Toss,', '- Pet Friendly', '- Easy walking distance of shopping, schools, parks, restaurants, hiking trails and transportation', '- Hiking trails galore..', '- Bike Fix it Spot', '- Barbeque Pool Side w/ Fire Pit', '- Spacious one and two bedroom apartments', '- Amazing School Districts', '- Recently Remodeled Pool, Clubhouse and Mini Gym,', '- Situated on lushly landscaped grounds', '- Parking Included', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets Ok With Additional Pet Deposit of $500 and Monthly Pet Rent of $60.00 each month.', '(Two Pet Maximum, Breed Restrictions Apply)', 'Income Requirements:', 'NA', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Parkside', '101 Sunnyhills Drive, San Anselmo, CA, 94960', '1HI3URdq']
